<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CCE 보안 점검 보고서 - {{ asset_info.hostname }}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        {{ inline_css }}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="report-header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>네트워크 장비 CCE 보안 점검 보고서</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Network Device CCE Compliance Assessment Report</p>
            </div>
            <div class="header-meta">
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <span class="label">보고서 생성일:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ report_date }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <span class="label">점검 도구:</span>
                    <span class="value">AI CCE Inspector v{{ tool_version }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Executive Summary -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>요약 (Executive Summary)</h2>
            <div class="summary-grid">
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="card-icon compliance-{{ 'pass' if summary.compliance_percentage >= 80 else 'warn' if summary.compliance_percentage >= 60 else 'fail' }}">
                        <span class="percentage">{{ "%.1f"|format(summary.compliance_percentage) }}%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-label">전체 준수율</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="card-value pass">{{ summary.passed }}</div>
                    <div class="card-label">통과</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="card-value fail">{{ summary.failed }}</div>
                    <div class="card-label">실패</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="card-value warn">{{ summary.not_configured }}</div>
                    <div class="card-label">미설정</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="severity-breakdown">
                <h3>심각도별 실패 현황</h3>
                <div class="severity-bars">
                    <div class="severity-bar critical">
                        <span class="severity-label">긴급 (Critical)</span>
                        <div class="bar-container">
                            <div class="bar-fill" style="width: {{ (summary.critical_failures / summary.total_checks * 100) if summary.total_checks > 0 else 0 }}%"></div>
                            <span class="bar-count">{{ summary.critical_failures }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="severity-bar high">
                        <span class="severity-label">높음 (High)</span>
                        <div class="bar-container">
                            <div class="bar-fill" style="width: {{ (summary.high_failures / summary.total_checks * 100) if summary.total_checks > 0 else 0 }}%"></div>
                            <span class="bar-count">{{ summary.high_failures }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="severity-bar medium">
                        <span class="severity-label">중간 (Medium)</span>
                        <div class="bar-container">
                            <div class="bar-fill" style="width: {{ (summary.medium_failures / summary.total_checks * 100) if summary.total_checks > 0 else 0 }}%"></div>
                            <span class="bar-count">{{ summary.medium_failures }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="severity-bar low">
                        <span class="severity-label">낮음 (Low)</span>
                        <div class="bar-container">
                            <div class="bar-fill" style="width: {{ (summary.low_failures / summary.total_checks * 100) if summary.total_checks > 0 else 0 }}%"></div>
                            <span class="bar-count">{{ summary.low_failures }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Asset Information -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>자산 정보 (Asset Information)</h2>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">호스트명:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ asset_info.hostname }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">제조사:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ asset_info.vendor|upper }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">OS 타입:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ asset_info.os_type|upper }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">OS 버전:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ asset_info.os_version }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">장비 유형:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ asset_info.device_type|capitalize }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">장비 역할:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ asset_info.device_role|replace('_', ' ')|title }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Critical Findings -->
        {% if critical_findings %}
        <section class="section critical-section">
            <h2>⚠️ 긴급 조치 필요 항목 (Critical Findings)</h2>
            <div class="findings-list">
                {% for finding in critical_findings %}
                <div class="finding-card critical">
                    <div class="finding-header">
                        <span class="finding-id">{{ finding.check_id }}</span>
                        <h3>{{ finding.title }}</h3>
                        <span class="badge badge-critical">CRITICAL</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="finding-body">
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>평가 결과:</strong>
                            <p>{{ finding.findings.evaluation }}</p>
                        </div>
                        {% if finding.findings.evidence %}
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>발견된 설정:</strong>
                            <pre class="code-block">{{ finding.findings.evidence|join('\n') }}</pre>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>권장사항:</strong>
                            <p>{{ finding.recommendation }}</p>
                        </div>
                        {% if finding.remediation_commands %}
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>조치 명령어:</strong>
                            <pre class="code-block remediation">{{ finding.remediation_commands|join('\n') }}</pre>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </section>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- All Findings by Category -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>점검 결과 상세 (Detailed Findings)</h2>

            {% for category_name, category_findings in findings_by_category.items() %}
            <div class="category-section">
                <h3 class="category-title">{{ category_name }}</h3>

                {% for finding in category_findings %}
                <div class="finding-card {{ 'pass' if finding.status == 'PASS' else 'fail' if finding.status == 'FAIL' else 'warn' }}">
                    <div class="finding-header">
                        <span class="finding-id">{{ finding.check_id }}</span>
                        <h4>{{ finding.title }}</h4>
                        <span class="badge badge-{{ finding.severity }}">{{ finding.severity|upper }}</span>
                        <span class="status-badge status-{{ finding.status|lower }}">{{ finding.status }}</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="finding-body">
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>평가:</strong>
                            <p>{{ finding.findings.evaluation }}</p>
                        </div>

                        {% if finding.findings.evidence %}
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>증거:</strong>
                            <pre class="code-block">{{ finding.findings.evidence|join('\n') }}</pre>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}

                        {% if finding.findings.criteria_met %}
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>✓ 충족된 조건:</strong>
                            <ul class="criteria-list pass">
                                {% for criteria in finding.findings.criteria_met %}
                                <li>{{ criteria }}</li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}

                        {% if finding.findings.criteria_failed %}
                        <div class="finding-section">
                            <strong>✗ 미충족 조건:</strong>
                            <ul class="criteria-list fail">
                                {% for criteria in finding.findings.criteria_failed %}
                                <li>{{ criteria }}</li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}

                        {% if finding.status != 'PASS' %}
                        <div class="finding-section recommendation">
                            <strong>권장사항:</strong>
                            <p>{{ finding.recommendation }}</p>

                            {% if finding.remediation_commands %}
                            <strong>조치 명령어:</strong>
                            <pre class="code-block remediation">{{ finding.remediation_commands|join('\n') }}</pre>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="report-footer">
            <p>본 보고서는 AI CCE Inspector를 통해 자동 생성되었습니다.</p>
            <p>This report was automatically generated by AI CCE Inspector.</p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                면책사항: 본 보고서는 참고용이며, 최종 보안 판단은 전문가의 검토가 필요합니다.
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
